CHAT.comment: Chi and Mot work together during this activity , and Chi's older Sis joins in here and there. They mostly engage in pretend play with the objects , though at one point Chi and Mot experiment with which magnets will stick to others. The only science talk is their discovery that the coins are not magnetic. Videotape does not start until later; transcript until then is solely from audio
